    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/05a07fd6d852d439f84fb7723ddd0fe5.poster.avif?t=1754506909\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/05a07fd6d852d439f84fb7723ddd0fe5.webm?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/05a07fd6d852d439f84fb7723ddd0fe5.mp4?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into your new home, a ring transport station in a lawless system commonly called 'Isfetian Space' on the edge of Federation territory. Most people say running a warp gate station in Isfetian Space is too dangerous and won't be profitable, but you didn't listen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/5959a4aefea8aedd1621e23f24150fc7.poster.avif?t=1754506909\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/5959a4aefea8aedd1621e23f24150fc7.webm?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/5959a4aefea8aedd1621e23f24150fc7.mp4?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Federation doesn't care what happens on the galaxy's fringe, but a ship that wants to travel back into the safer core systems needs clean credentials. That's where you come in! Earn the trust of The Federation by sending ships that have cleared credentials, exposing counterfeit credentials, and reporting wanted individuals to the Federation Police. Send too many uncleared ships and you'll lose the trust of The Federation, and your access to the core systems, leaving you with a warp gate and nowhere to send ships!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/796dc57c340c5bf14f219ac217d73791.poster.avif?t=1754506909\" width=800 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/796dc57c340c5bf14f219ac217d73791.webm?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135620/extras/796dc57c340c5bf14f219ac217d73791.mp4?t=1754506909\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Core mechanics: </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send ships through the warp gate to generate income</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain the station and keep it in tip-top shape</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect resources to craft parts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hack into a ship's computers to validate credentials and expose counterfeits</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Place and send tracking data on flagged ships and report wanted individuals to gain Federation trust</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the asteroid field and uncover its secrets</p></li></ul>",
